creator: Adolo
descriptionHtml:
The main features of this app include the following:

AUDIO SERMONS
Listen to over 1,800 sermons by Dr. David Oyedepo.

ADD TO FAVORITE
Use the provided round checkboxes to add your favorite audio sermons to your favorite list.

AUDIO BOOKS
Listen to audio books by Dr. David Oyedepo.

E-BOOKS
Read inspiring E-Books by Dr. David Oyedepo and other christian authors. The E-book reader tracks your reading progress and automatically stores the page where you stopped. The page will be presented to you whenever you return, so you can continue reading from where you stopped.

DOMI RADIO
Listen to live broadcast of christian music, sermons and other inspiring christian programs.

LIVE VIDEO BROADCAST
Watch live video broadcasts of Faith Tabernacle Church services featuring Dr. David Oyedepo and other ministers

QUOTES
The quotes have been grouped into 5 chapters, and each chapter contains 50 quotes; making a total of 250 quotes. The groupings and numbering makes it easy to reference any particular quote. You can also share your favourite quotes on the twitter and whatsapp.

NOTE: Internet or WiFi connection is required to stream audio messages (sermons), videos, radio stations and access other online contents.
descriptionShort: Read E-Books & Quotes, Listen to Audio Books & over 1,800 Sermons
